## Control Panel Reference

| Control | Mode | What it does |
|---------|------|--------------|
| [ AUTO ] | Any | Switch to auto mode — thresholds control fan/buzzer |
| [ MANUAL ] | Any | Switch to manual mode — fan controlled by toggle |
| Fan Override toggle | Manual only | Turn fan ON or OFF directly |
| STOP FAN button | Auto | Cancel running 20s fan timer |
| Alarm Mute toggle | Auto | Silence buzzer without stopping the timer |
| STOP BUZZ button | Auto | Cancel running 20s buzzer timer |
| ⚠ EMERGENCY STOP | Any | Immediately kill fan + buzzer + LED |

