## Countdown Timers

When the fan or buzzer 20-second timer is running, countdown badges appear directly on the metric cards:

```
Fan card:   [ AUTO OFF IN  17 SEC ]
Alarm card: [ BUZZER OFF IN 12 SEC ]
```

The terminal bar at the top also shows:
```
FAN_TIMER: 17s | BUZZ_TIMER: 12s
```

These values come from Firebase — the ESP32 pushes `fanRemaining` and `buzzerRemaining` fields every second.

