## Customization

All color variables are in CSS `:root`:

```css
:root {
  --g1: #00ff41;   /* Primary green — metric values */
  --r:  #ff0040;   /* Red — alarms and danger */
  --o:  #ff6600;   /* Orange — warnings and countdowns */
  --y:  #ffdd00;   /* Yellow — warnings */
  --c:  #00ffcc;   /* Cyan — info and badges */
}
```

Gas/temp thresholds displayed in the UI (bottom of alert history panel):
- Gas alarm: 700 raw ADC
- Fan ON: 35°C
- Buzzer/Fan timer: 20 seconds

