## Troubleshooting

| Problem | Cause | Fix |
|---------|-------|-----|
| Firebase badge stays red | Wrong credentials or rules | Check API key + set Firebase rules to read/write true |
| ESP32 badge stays red | No data in `/sensors` | Check ESP32 is running and pushing to Firebase |
| Railway badge red | Wrong URL or backend down | Check Railway dashboard, verify URL has no trailing slash |
| Control buttons do nothing | Railway disconnected | Check Railway badge is green first |
| Countdown timer doesn't show | Firebase push not working | Check ESP32 is pushing `fanRemaining`/`buzzerRemaining` |
| Charts not updating | Firebase listener failed | Refresh page, re-initialize |
| Config modal keeps appearing | RAILWAY field empty | Fill in Railway URL and click Initialize |

